				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I get a couple sprites missing from the screen too, but not nearly a whole column missing like you appear to be getting. The pair moves after every reset, and occasionally they're all bunched up at the top or at the left. It might have something to do with what I discovered while making Concentration Room: OAM refresh isn't in a defined state immediately after reset; you have to let one frame finish rendering before OAM refresh becomes stable. The best practice is to copy OAM after one complete frame has been displayed. This happens automatically in an actual game such as MineShaft, where OAM is copied during each vblank.<br /><br />I'll make a test ROM for this exact bad practice, where the user can manually force OAM to be recopied.<br /><br /><br />EDIT: Here's the test. It's bigger than lidnariq's because it includes full source code.</div>

					
